    "description": "<p>\r\n\t<strong>Singapore G Pte Ltd was founded in 1973. Our motto is to responsibly provide our customers with value added services at a fair price. </strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>Besides offering grade A warehouse and office space, the company is continuously looking at ways to provide complementary services to our customers. We provide self-storage facilities under U-Store@SG where customers may rent storage space from as little as 10 sq. ft. on a monthly basis.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>Serviced offices, meeting rooms, briefing and board rooms are also available for short term lease and hourly hire under MustardSeed@SG. Providing maximum flexibility to every business need. TreeTops Sports Gym allows an avenue for one to keep physically and mentally fit.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>Singapore G provides for all kinds of business space requirements under one roof.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>Singapore G not only invest in brick and mortar facilities, but also develop our human resources. Staffs are briefed on current regulatory developments, trained in first aid; and are required to maintain a standard of fitness and vigilance to better serve our tenants.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t </p>\r\n",
